  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DatabaseOperation

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DatabaseSetup
    Indicates how to put a database into a know state before tests are run.
    DatabaseTearDown
    Indicates how to put a database into a know state after tests have run.
    DbUnitConfiguration
    Configures a test run.
    ExpectedDatabase
    Asserts that a database is in given state after tests have run.
